sub_title: French teacher with a Project Manager background
summary:
Relevant skills
Curriculum planning
Finding and/or creating new learning material related with the interests and level of the student to keep them involved
Reorganize and prioritize the lesson depending of the goal

Customer oriented
Taylor made curriculum and lessons to answer the need
Adapt the curriculum and the method to assure the best progression
Able to connect quickly with people

Adaptive and proactive
Entrepreneurial mindset: Not afraid of new challenges
Lived and worked in several countries (France, England, Germany, Switzerland, Netherland)
Able to switch quickly and to review the strategy in order to move on
Flexible and creative

Project management
Enjoys finding solutions
Budget management
Meeting deadlines
Scheduling activities
Strong communicator
